dcterms:description: A protein function prediction challenge dataset containing training sequences and functional annotations represented by functional terms of the hierarchical structure of the Gene Ontology (GO). The dataset was filtered to include only relevant proteins and functions, resulting in a reduced ontology with 123 nodes and 145 edges.
